# Session-artifact storage — code in git, rendered output in Dropbox.
# See docs/decisions/2026-06-15-session-artifact-storage.md (tag: session-artifact-storage).
#
# Only AUTHORED artifacts belong here (.bkr / .py / .md / session.json). RENDERED
# artifacts live in Dropbox; this ignore is a belt-and-braces catch for a stray
# render accidentally written under sessions/ so it never bloats git history.
*.png
*.svg
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.log
*.err
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.DS_Store
# Large generated JSON (geometry truth + cluster output) — regenerable, stays in Dropbox.
pattern.gt.json
clusters.json
*.gt.json
# Backups
*.bak
